data.description: Check out this open concept ranch, built in 2018.  You'll love the kitchen with espresso cabinet, large center island, Stainless steel appliances, quartz counters & tile backsplash. Living and dining space is generous and offers new luxury vinyl flooring. The master suite features a large shower, 2 vanities and a walk-in closet. Bright second bedroom next to the 2nd bathroom.  The home has a massive unfinished basement.  Lots of storage.  The home offers a deck and fenced in yard.  The home is close to parks, schools, shopping.  Easy access to highways.
